data.description: WOW! Take a look at this completely remodeled single-level home! Situated on a large flat lot in a great neighborhood, this beautiful ranch style home offers modern esthetics throughout. Starting with the white brick and stunning black accents as soon as you pull into your driveway! Inside you will find an open-concept living area with a spacious dining room (check out those gorgeous beams!) a functional kitchen with a massive custom island, all overlooking your family room with vaulted ceilings and plenty of lighting! Walking down the hallway you will find 2 adorable bedrooms and a remodeled full bath with gorgeous tile work and tub! Along with your stunning master suite that boasts plenty of space, a walk in closet and another beautiful full bathroom with a walk-in shower! As if that isn't enough, just wait until you step out into your backyard oasis! Offering an 8ft tall privacy fenced, PLENTY of room for the kiddos to run and play, and your very own semi-inground pool with a covered sitting area and bar! WOW! Updated in 2021- flooring, windows, cabinets, appliances, lighting, bathrooms, and more.
